Module com.bcs2024.knapsack
Package com.bcs2024.knapsack.model

Class CargoSpace

java.lang.Object
com.bcs2024.knapsack.model.CargoSpace
public class CargoSpace extends Object
Represents a three-dimensional cargo space in the context of a knapsack problem. The CargoSpace class manages parcel placements, dimensions of the cargo space, and tracks the state of occupied slots within the cargo space.

  • Constructor Details

    • CargoSpace

      public CargoSpace()
      Constructs a new CargoSpace object representing a three-dimensional cargo space. This constructor initializes the dimensions (x, y, z) based on the width, height, and length, and creates an occupied array to represent the cargo space, initializing all elements to -1.
